m_messages_tuple` - 需要 dev server\n   - 这两个测试需要启动 `langgraph dev` 服务，由于没有 Docker 环境无法运行\n\n3. **跳过的测试**:\n   - PostgreSQL 相关测试 (需要 Docker 运行 postgres)\n   - Redis 相关测试 (需要 Docker 运行 redis)\n\n### 结论\n\n✅ **配置成功** - 所有核心库依赖已安装，lint/format 检查通过，单元测试大部分通过。失败项均为需要外部服务 (PostgreSQL/Redis/dev server) 的测试，非代码问题。","time":{"start":1775800006697,"end":1775800006697},"id":"prt_d75ed940c002PKibf7pKUhWQS6","sessionID":"ses_28a1d194dffeV6NdtTaUN1GyyK","messageID":"msg_d75ed8ea5001eEigjO6GLGzriV"},{"reason":"stop","snapshot":"d32c9b1e4058c46c110a7101578265d35fb49359","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":34323,"input":33805,"output":518,"reasoning":5,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0,"id":"prt_d75edb82e001p9bA2QHZD8uZC5","sessionID":"ses_28a1d194dffeV6NdtTaUN1GyyK","messageID":"msg_d75ed8ea5001eEigjO6GLGzriV"}]}}
